&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>Pinecone is a managed vector database that provides vector search (or “similarity search”) for developers with a straightforward API and usage-based pricing. It’s free to try. &lt;a href="https://www.pinecone.io/learn/vector-search-basics/" target="_blank">Introduction to Vector Search for Developers&lt;/a>.&lt;/p>
